FC GR Cc Bill NonPrivilegedpst I too am for moving up Also I play pickup with a group of people three or four of whom could really help us heighten the level of play if I can recruit them As for practices Justin Kerr and coach the varsity boys at Oregon Episcopal School off SW Scolls Ferry Rd Our fall practices run until PM after which the Green Room may be able use the fields Justin is chummy with the Athletic Director so well see what we can do theyre pretty nice fields IN OTHER NEWS I am in the process of moving This weekend I found a beautiful BR BA house in the SW hills on a big chunk of land Its got a garage terraced lawn wood floors etc However I dont have three roommates If anyone on the team or their friends is looking for a place let me know if they might be interested in pursuing this house Its month util dep for each of the four people Adam Van Loon Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at
